Title: Distributed monitoring respects InfluxDB site restriction rule
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: setup
Date: 1684747470
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0p31

Previously all configured InfluxDB connections were enabled on all remote
configured sites, despite limiting a connection to specific sites.
With this release the problem is eliminated.
